<Layout title="Fast and Reliable Video Game Collections" description="Myrient - Fast and reliable video game preservation with organized collections for download.">
  <h1>Myrient - Fast and Reliable Video Game Collections</h1>
  <h2>A Myriad of Entertainment</h2>
  <hr />
  <p>
    Myrient is a fast and reliable video game preservation service with over 390 terabytes of
    organized collections publicly available for download.
  </p>
  <p>We offer the following features:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>No account required</strong> - No registration is needed to download content.</li>
    <li><strong>No paywalls</strong> - We do not charge for access.</li>
    <li><strong>No advertisements shown</strong> - We do not serve advertisements anywhere on Myrient.</li>
    <li><strong>Download managers supported</strong> - Myrient can be used with most download managers. Check the FAQ for more information.</li>
    <li><strong>Download files in quick succession</strong> - We do not make you wait in between downloads.</li>
    <li><strong>Multiple concurrent downloads</strong> - We do not limit the number of files you can download at a time.</li>
    <li><strong>Fast downloads</strong> - We use high-end servers for the best performance possible.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2>A Myriad of Difference</h2>
  <hr />
  <p>
    Many ROM and archive websites show too many advertisements, pop-ups, and paywalls while
    requiring users to create an account to download content.
  </p>
  <p>
    Myrient sets the standard for video game preservation and takes a different approach by
    focusing on accessibility. We understand that a bad user experience can be frustrating and
    that video game preservation is only as effective as the means of access.
  </p>
  <p>
    <a href="/files/">Browse files →</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
